rule1: Talk about the right subject in the right channel.
rule2: Any form of advertising is strictly forbidden, **MP included**, unless an exception is authorised after request.
rule5: No insults, disrespect, vulgar words, provocation, threats, nsfw content, etc.
rule6: Don't usurp someone's identity by using the same profile picture and/or nickname.
rule7: It is forbidden to release any personal information about someone without their consent.
rule8: Don't bring double accounts. Only one account per user on the server is sufficient.
rule9: Make an effort to write correctly, use the spell checker if necessary.
rule10: It is forbidden to raid other servers.
rule11: It is forbidden to create, revive or talk about drama.
rule13: Avoid talking about external affairs, particularly those related to other servers, on this server. They are none of our concern.
